Class RoThroJoint

  • Constructor Details

    • RoThroJoint

      public RoThroJoint(String t, double linDampg, double b1Speed, double b2Speed, double upLim, double lowLim, double angDampg, double dist, double mMotF, double mMotT, double speed, double f, org.dyn4j.geometry.Vector2 axis, org.dyn4j.geometry.Vector2 anchorPnt1, org.dyn4j.geometry.Vector2 anchorPnt2, Obstacle b1, Obstacle b2, boolean limEn)
      Construct a new RoThro joint based on various parameters.
      Parameters:
      t - joint type
      linDampg - desired linear damping (for springs)
      b1Speed - desired speed for body1 (for Prismatic Joint)
      b2Speed - desired speed for body2 (for Prismatic Joint)
      upLim - upper Limit constraint for movement (All Joints)
      lowLim - lower Limit constraint for movement (All Joints)
      angDampg - desired linear damping (for hinges)
      dist - desired distance for rest pos (springs)
      mMotF - max motor force (for springs and Prismatic Joints)
      mMotT - max motor torque (for hinges and pendulum)
      speed - desired motor speed (prismatic joint)
      f - frequency of spring joint (stiffness)
      axis - axis along which bodies move (Prismatic Joint)
      anchorPnt1 - anchor pnt1 (for all Joints)
      anchorPnt2 - anchor pnt2 (for all Joints)
      b1 - Obstacle 1
      b2 - Obstacle 2
      limEn - whether limits are enabled
